---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page
  title="About | Botify Life"
  description="Learn more about Botify Life, our mission, and how we help you improve your lifestyle with automation and AI."
  pageUrl="/about"
>
  <main class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-50 to-white min-h-screen pt-20 pb-12 px-4">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 mt-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">About Botify Life</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6 text-center">
        Botify Life is dedicated to empowering individuals and businesses to improve their lifestyle and productivity through automation, AI, and customizable bots.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our mission is to make advanced automation and AI accessible to everyone. We believe in giving you the tools to create, manage, and scale bots and agents that help you achieve more with less effort.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2">What We Offer</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Easy-to-use platform for creating and managing MCP servers and agents</li>
            <li>Flexible pricing plans for every stage of your journey</li>
            <li>LLM (Large Language Model) usage: pay per token or use your own API key</li>
            <li>Professional support and a growing community</li>
            <li>Opportunity to earn: create and sell your MCP servers and agents, with only a 20% commission fee</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2">Opportunity for Earning</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            You can create and sell your own MCP servers and agents on our platform. We only charge a 20% commission, so you keep 80% of your earnings. Empower others while building your own business!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-2">Why Choose Botify Life?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Modern, accessible, and responsive design</li>
            <li>Transparent pricing and flexible billing</li>
            <li>Focus on privacy, security, and user empowerment</li>
            <li>Continuous updates and new features</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>